  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 47a621783cb453147b01764dde5ed130, type: 3}
  m_Name: 4_RestoreHeartgrove
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - Now it must be returned to the Heartgrove deep within the Enchanted Forest.
  - That place is the heart of the magical world bound to this meadow.
  - For generations, Moonwardens protected it...
  - But over time, the magic grew weaker than any of us realized.
  - Go, dear. The forest is waiting.
  - Bring the Moonheart Elixir to the Heartgrove.
  - The meadow's future depends on it.
  - You did it, dear. You restored the magic.
  - I couldn't be more proud of you.
